title: Newbie
description: It might be time for a Husky history lesson. Don't worry, there are lots of die-hards in Seattle who will be happy to reminisce about the glory days.

title: Husky fan in training
description: You clearly know enough to pass as a true fan, but you've got some learning to do.

title: Seasoned fan
description: There's no question you're a member of the Husky faithful. You can't wait to pull that purple and gold windbreaker from 1985 out and head to Montlake this fall.

title: Dawgfather
description: Maybe you can teach us a thing or two about the Huskies, oh wise Dawgfather.
